when I met her.

00:02:58.058 --> 00:02:59.558
Hey, Takatoo...

00:02:59.591 --> 00:03:01.258
Yeah?

00:03:01.291 --> 00:03:04.958
Is this place really haunted
or is it just an empty building?

00:03:04.991 --> 00:03:07.058
This place is
haunted all right...

00:03:07.091 --> 00:03:09.258
I have it on good authority
that 3 years ago,

00:03:09.291 --> 00:03:12.891
a gang of bank robbers used
this place as a hideout.

00:03:12.925 --> 00:03:14.958
But when the cops were
catching up with them,

00:03:14.991 --> 00:03:18.558
one of the members freaked out,
thinking they were done for.

00:03:25.358 --> 00:03:27.591
The fire spread
in an instant.

00:03:27.625 --> 00:03:29.091
And they weren't the
only people here.

00:03:29.125 --> 00:03:30.891
Some people were
burned to death.

00:03:30.925 --> 00:03:32.391
Others died jumping
from the windows,

00:03:32.425 --> 00:03:34.391
trying to escape
the blaze.

00:03:34.425 --> 00:03:36.158
Not too long
after that,

00:03:36.191 --> 00:03:37.858
a strange rumor
started going around

00:03:37.891 --> 00:03:39.925
that some kids who went
to play in the scorched ruins

00:03:39.958 --> 00:03:41.258
never came out.

00:03:41.291 --> 00:03:42.958
And when some adults
went in to look for them,

00:03:42.991 --> 00:03:44.391
they didn't
come out, either.

00:03:44.425 --> 00:03:46.458
Everyone vanished.

00:03:46.491 --> 00:03:48.425
Soon, companies started
turning down orders

00:03:48.458 --> 00:03:50.291
to demolish
what was left.

00:03:50.325 --> 00:03:52.458
After a while, some people
gave the building a name

00:03:52.491 --> 00:03:54.391
they thought it deserved.

00:03:54.425 --> 00:03:57.058
They call it "the
man-eating building."

00:03:57.091 --> 00:03:59.025
[Screeming]

00:03:59.058 --> 00:04:00.958
You guys have
to be careful.

00:04:00.991 --> 00:04:02.458
I'm used to being
in this kind of environment,

00:04:02.491 --> 00:04:04.558
but it can be
dangerous in here.

00:04:04.591 --> 00:04:05.425
Okay.

00:04:05.458 --> 00:04:07.558
Hey, man. I'm guessing
this is the room

00:04:07.591 --> 00:04:10.625
where the bank robbers hid
and ended up biting the dust?

00:04:10.658 --> 00:04:13.225
Yeah... You can
feel it, can't you?

00:04:13.258 --> 00:04:14.191
Such incredible energy.

00:04:14.225 --> 00:04:15.191
Really?

00:04:15.225 --> 00:04:16.925
Yeah, really.

00:04:19.025 --> 00:04:21.325
You should be leaving now.

00:04:21.358 --> 00:04:23.325
This place is dangerous.

00:04:23.358 --> 00:04:24.958
I'll just stick
with you...

00:04:24.991 --> 00:04:26.358
Wait up!

00:04:32.258 --> 00:04:33.591
No...

00:04:33.625 --> 00:04:35.558
What's wrong?

00:04:35.591 --> 00:04:37.991
I thought I saw
a dead body right there.

00:04:38.025 --> 00:04:39.158
No you didn't...

00:04:39.191 --> 00:04:42.091
They cleaned all
that out a long time ago.

00:04:44.091 --> 00:04:45.358
Well, look at that...

00:04:45.391 --> 00:04:46.558
It's just a dummy.

00:04:46.591 --> 00:04:49.258
Must be some kind
of practical joke.

00:04:49.291 --> 00:04:50.858
I'm not a spiritual guy,

00:04:50.891 --> 00:04:53.258
but this has gotta be
disrespectful to the dead.

00:04:53.291 --> 00:04:54.358
That looks like
real cash, man.

