It's fake.

00:04:57.991 --> 00:05:00.125
Don't!

00:05:00.158 --> 00:05:03.425
Put the money back and
step away from there!

00:05:03.458 --> 00:05:05.291
Hey, you're that chick.

00:05:05.325 --> 00:05:08.091
Give it back...

00:05:08.125 --> 00:05:09.958
Give it back...

00:05:09.991 --> 00:05:11.125
It's mine...

00:05:11.158 --> 00:05:12.925
My money...

00:05:12.958 --> 00:05:14.158
Give it back...

00:05:14.191 --> 00:05:15.491
Give it back...

00:05:15.525 --> 00:05:17.425
Give it back!

00:05:20.925 --> 00:05:24.191
What're you doing?!
Get outta here!

00:05:24.225 --> 00:05:25.925
Just keep running to
the end of the hallway!

00:05:25.958 --> 00:05:28.258
It'll get you
outside...! Go!

00:05:28.291 --> 00:05:30.458
The bastards
stole my money...

00:05:30.491 --> 00:05:34.091
And I'm gonna
kill them...

00:05:34.125 --> 00:05:37.358
Hold on to me!

00:05:37.391 --> 00:05:38.925
We gotta hurry.

00:05:38.958 --> 00:05:41.358
This is my money!

00:05:48.225 --> 00:05:51.258
What happened...?!
Are you okay?

00:05:51.291 --> 00:05:52.491
She's dead?

00:05:52.525 --> 00:05:55.425
Oh, no!
She's dead!

00:05:57.891 --> 00:06:00.091
I'm gonna kill you all.

00:06:04.291 --> 00:06:06.858
You're not getting away!

00:06:22.325 --> 00:06:25.358
And now you die
like the rest!

00:06:36.158 --> 00:06:39.858
When someone dies with strong
regrets, they become Shikabane.

00:06:39.891 --> 00:06:41.525
They're corpses
who curse living people

00:06:41.558 --> 00:06:43.891
and set their sights
on killing them.

00:06:43.925 --> 00:06:45.325
I've heard talk
that there are people

00:06:45.358 --> 00:06:48.358
who want to get rid of us
using other Shikabane.

00:06:48.391 --> 00:06:51.425
Which must be what you are!

00:06:51.458 --> 00:06:54.391
One who tries
to kill immortals?!

00:06:54.425 --> 00:06:57.191
Damn you...!
If I knew you weren't human,

00:06:57.225 --> 00:06:59.258
I would've skipped
those other worthless kids

00:06:59.291 --> 00:07:01.158
and killed
your ass first!

00:07:03.325 --> 00:07:05.858
In that moment,
I was calmly amazed

00:07:05.891 --> 00:07:08.458
that it wasn't fear
or surprise filling my heart.

00:07:08.491 --> 00:07:10.191
I was captivated.

00:07:10.225 --> 00:07:13.525
Held tight in the wake of beauty
left behind that fighting girl.

00:07:13.558 --> 00:07:15.958
People have said from the
beginning of humanity

00:07:15.991 --> 00:07:18.558
that death is something
of which to be frightened.

00:07:18.591 --> 00:07:21.558
I've thought that perhaps
that's not entirely true.

00:07:21.591 --> 00:07:24.425
Because death releases
people from this world.

00:07:24.458 --> 00:07:27.458
And yes, her beauty
is the beauty of death.

00:07:27.491 --> 00:07:29.591
The beauty of release.

00:07:54.425 --> 00:07:56.191
Since that day,
I've wanted more than anything

00:07:56.225 --> 00:07:59.158
to see her
just one more time.

00:07:59.191 --> 00:08:01.358
I wonder why.

00:08:06.325 --> 00:08:07.558
No matter
how hard I searched,

00:08:07.591 --> 00:08:10.358
I could never
find a Shikabane.

00:08:10.391 --> 00:08:13.325
More importantly,
I could never find her.

00:08:25.325 --> 00:08:27.858
I can't believe it!
It's her!

00:08:29.491 --> 00:08:31.591
I've told you
over and over again... .

00:08:31.625 --> 00:08:34.591
Do not get
involved with us!

00:08:34.625 --> 00:08:36.191
I know
what you've said...

00:08:36.225 --> 00:08:38.358
But I have to know
where Minai was taken...

00:08:38.391 --> 00:08:40.991
Why can't you
just tell me that?

00:08:41.025 --> 00:08:42.591
Minai...?
Who's that?

00:08:42.625 --> 00:08:45.358
Come on... You know
who I'm talking about!

00:08:45.391 --> 00:08:47.525
Actually,
Ouri, I don't.

00:08:49.891 --> 00:08:51.458
Did you kill her?!

00:08:54.191 --> 00:08:57.391
I don't know anything because
we didn't do anything.

00:08:57.425 --> 00:09:00.291
Keisei said it was resolved,
which is good enough for me.

00:09:00.325 --> 00:09:02.325
It should be good
enough for you, too.

00:09:02.358 --> 00:09:04.625
Don't lie to me...!
Where did she go?!

00:09:04.658 --> 00:09:06.825
Give me
a straight answer!

00:09:13.325 --> 00:09:15.358
Thanks...

00:09:18.025 --> 00:09:19.925
I think
I remember him...

00:09:19.958 --> 00:09:22.191
Hi there.

00:09:22.225 --> 00:09:23.991
Are you a
friend of Ouri's?

00:09:24.025 --> 00:09:25.458
Um... Well...

00:09:25.491 --> 00:09:27.425
I guess you
could say that...

00:09:28.958 --> 00:09:31.025
Bye!

00:09:31.058 --> 00:09:33.325
What a weird girl.

00:09:36.991 --> 00:09:37.858
I don't know, Ouri.

00:09:37.891 --> 00:09:39.258
