But next year,
I'll be the president

00:10:10.458 --> 00:10:12.058
and you will
all be my staff.

00:10:12.091 --> 00:10:14.191
We'll carry out
glorious reformations!

00:10:14.225 --> 00:10:17.091
We alone will craft a golden
era for Ikai High School...

00:10:17.125 --> 00:10:19.491
Hey...! Pay attention
when I'm talking to you!

00:10:19.525 --> 00:10:20.558
While it looks like you

00:10:20.591 --> 00:10:23.058
two suckers are busy
riding the depression train,

00:10:23.091 --> 00:10:24.391
I'm gonna show
you something today

00:10:24.425 --> 00:10:27.591
that will instantly make all of
your problems a distant memory.

