00:10:36.091 --> 00:10:37.925
What do you
mean so what...?!

00:10:37.958 --> 00:10:40.891
It should be obvious.
That woman is a Breast Goddess!

00:10:40.925 --> 00:10:43.225
Breast Goddess?

00:10:43.258 --> 00:10:46.158
See? I mean,
would you look at that!

00:10:51.458 --> 00:10:53.925
There's nothing wrong with
focusing our infatuations

00:10:53.958 --> 00:10:56.525
on hot models or TV stars
or anime voice actors

00:10:56.558 --> 00:10:57.658
or even transfer students.

00:10:57.691 --> 00:11:00.258
But I thought I'd go back
to when it all began for me.

00:11:00.291 --> 00:11:01.891
The goddess who's
drawn my attention

00:11:01.925 --> 00:11:03.491
since I started
high school.

00:11:03.525 --> 00:11:05.291
And she's bigger than
that transfer student!

00:11:05.325 --> 00:11:06.925
Isn't she hot?
Don't you feel better?

