He seems to think,
for whatever reason,

00:11:54.387 --> 00:11:57.554
that Makina is his
brother's girlfriend.

00:11:57.587 --> 00:11:59.921
Would he be close to
the truth on that?

00:11:59.954 --> 00:12:02.754
No, not a chance...

00:12:02.787 --> 00:12:06.454
although I don't know how
Makina feels about it.

00:12:07.687 --> 00:12:10.854
She's a Shikabane Hime.
