Ouri...

00:12:17.454 --> 00:12:19.654
Ouri...

00:12:19.687 --> 00:12:21.287
What's wrong with you?!

00:12:21.321 --> 00:12:23.021
Hello.

00:12:23.054 --> 00:12:24.921
Ouri, I would like
to introduce you

00:12:24.954 --> 00:12:26.854
to my lovely
breast goddess.

00:12:26.887 --> 00:12:28.921
Breast, what?

