were good friends,

00:12:38.321 --> 00:12:39.487
so I thought...

00:12:39.521 --> 00:12:41.254
We're friends...
I don't know how--

00:12:41.287 --> 00:12:42.887
It doesn't matter. Just let
me get right to the point,

00:12:42.921 --> 00:12:43.987
if you don't mind.

00:12:44.021 --> 00:12:45.621
Of course.

