00:13:04.421 --> 00:13:05.787
Yeah...

00:13:05.821 --> 00:13:08.554
but I think it'd be better
if you stay away from her.

00:13:08.587 --> 00:13:10.354
I don't understand. Why?

00:13:10.387 --> 00:13:13.287
It's complicated...
Because...

00:13:13.321 --> 00:13:16.854
Shikabane Hime attract
those who admire death.

00:13:16.887 --> 00:13:20.787
I wonder if this woman is
also fascinated by death...

00:13:20.821 --> 00:13:23.421
Just like you.

00:13:23.454 --> 00:13:26.254
Uh... is something wrong?

00:13:26.287 --> 00:13:28.454
It's nothing, sorry.

00:13:28.487 --> 00:13:30.554
In the same way
you're drawn to death,

00:13:30.587 --> 00:13:33.954
you're also drawn
to Shikabane Hime.

00:13:33.987 --> 00:13:36.821
You can no longer
get out of it.

00:13:36.854 --> 00:13:38.854
Shut up!

00:13:43.821 --> 00:13:46.621
Uh...

00:13:46.654 --> 00:13:49.721
Oh, no... I was just
trying to catch...

00:13:49.754 --> 00:13:51.687
a... cat.

