00:14:14.354 --> 00:14:16.654
with this kind
of crap from you!

00:14:20.421 --> 00:14:22.754
No one else
can see me...

00:14:22.787 --> 00:14:25.321
Because I am you...

00:14:29.854 --> 00:14:31.921
Here, I'm finished.

